---
title: Sausage and Sweet Potato Fries with Pancetta Beans
description: This deliciously comforting recipe proves that making your own homemade baked beans is totally worth it. Chef Lizzie has combined velvety butter beans with pancetta, sage, basil and finely chopped tomatoes for a flavour that you just can’t beat. Served with the best sausages and sweet potato fries, this dish is a complete dinner winner and is guaranteed to be a hit with everyone. Homemade comfort food doesn’t get better than this.
